# Frontend Rules

## Components

Use:

- Functional components
- Hooks
- Composition
- Custom hooks
- Suspense
- Error boundaries

Avoid:

- Class components
- Prop drilling
- Massive components
- Mixed responsibilities

Rules:

- Components ≤ 200 lines
- Move logic to hooks
- Keep render clean
- One responsibility per component

---

## Hooks

Rules:

- Prefix with use
- Keep focused
- Avoid side effects in render
- Extract reusable logic

Correct:

```tsx
const {users}=useUsers()
```

Avoid:

```tsx
const users=api.get()
```